## 2. Identify the user + track routing (FlowRouter)

`lib/shell/flow_router.dart` is the loading screen + gray/native decision.

- `initState` → `Insight.screen('loading');`
- Right after `assembleGateBody(...)` (where `af_id` is known), identify:

```dart
// inside _ask(), after body is assembled
Insight.identify(
  body['af_id']?.toString(),
  tags: {
    'af_status': body['af_status']?.toString() ?? '',
    'media_source': body['media_source']?.toString() ?? '',
    'campaign': body['campaign']?.toString() ?? '',
    'os': body['os']?.toString() ?? '',
    'locale': body['locale']?.toString() ?? '',
  },
);
```

- Tag the run mode + emit one event per routing branch, so the funnel
  starts at "which mode did this install get":
  - `_toWeb`   → `Insight.tag('run_mode','web'); Insight.event('route_web');`
  - `_goNative`→ `Insight.tag('run_mode','native'); Insight.event('route_native');`
  - `_toOffline`→ `Insight.event('route_offline');`
  - pending push link branch → `Insight.event('route_push_link');`
  - cached link branch → `Insight.event('route_cached_link');`

